DevModel.EngineeringDescription: The Battery Diagnostics System is composed of four main components - Site Information providing customer and location data, Battery Monitoring and Control providing measurements and control of the battery system, Device Status and Control providing status and control of the various devices in the system, and File Access providing access to historical data and system logs.

ReportDescriptor.EngineeringDescription: Monitor and Control of Battery System.
